"title": "5531: skill",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5531",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A trade or craft acquired by training or practice, or a special ability or expertise that may be an endowment of the Holy Spirit. Scripture lists many skills and abilities, particularly used in the building of the tabernacle and temple.</p>\n<h2>Skill offered in God's service</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:10\">EXO 35:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:15-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:15–22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:21\">1CH 28:21</a></p>\n<h2>Skill in particular crafts</h2>\n<h3>In working metal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:4\">JDG 17:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24\">ACT 19:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:14-1Kgs7:15\">1KI 7:14–7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:41-1Kgs7:45\">1KI 7:41–7:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:12-2Chr4:16\">2CH 4:12–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:5-2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:5–3:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:14\">2TI 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>In working stone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:2\">1CH 22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:15-1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:15–5:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:2\">2CH 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:36\">1KI 6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:9-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:9–7:12</a></p>\n<h3>With timber</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:6\">1KI 5:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:8-2Chr2:9\">2CH 2:8–2:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:14-1Kgs6:36\">1KI 6:14–6:36</a></p>\n<h3>With fabrics</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:36\">EXO 26:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:5\">EXO 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:1-Exod39:5\">EXO 39:1–39:5</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a> <em>skill in spinning</em></p>\n<h3>With music</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:22\">1CH 15:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:12-2Chr34:13\">2CH 34:12–34:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:3\">PSA 33:3</a></p>\n<h3>Other skills</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:27\">GEN 25:27</a> <em>hunting</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:27\">1KI 9:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:8\">EZK 27:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:22\">JOB 32:22</a> <em>flattery</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:1\">PSA 45:1</a> <em>writing</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:5\">PSA 58:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:3\">ISA 3:3</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:72\">PSA 78:72</a> <em>leadership</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:33\">JER 2:33</a> <em>love</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:17\">JER 9:17</a> <em>Mourning: professional mourners were a feature of life in Bible times</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:9\">JER 50:9</a> <em>fighting</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:5\">EZK 28:5</a> <em>trading</em></p>\n<h2>Undesirable skills</h2>\n<h3>In constructing idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:13\">ISA 44:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:19–40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:7\">ISA 41:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:2\">HOS 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:29\">ACT 17:29</a></p>\n<h3>Doing evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:11\">ISA 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:31\">EZK 21:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:3\">MIC 7:3</a></p>\n<h2>Acquiring skill</h2>\n<h3>Through training</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:18\">1CH 5:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14\">GEN 14:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:11\">2CH 26:11</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:7\">1CH 25:7</a> <em>musical skill</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:40\">LUK 6:40</a> <em>teaching abilities</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:25\">1CO 9:25</a> <em>Athletic prowess requires strict training</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:14\">HEB 5:14</a> <em>distinguishing good from evil through proper training</em></p>\n<h3>Skills given by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:1–31:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod35:35\">EXO 35:30–35:35</a> <em>These skills may well have been developed through training, but they are recognised as gifts from God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:1-Exod36:2\">EXO 36:1–36:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:11\">DEU 33:11</a> <em>Moses prays for Levi's skills to be blessed by God</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">ISA 50:4</a> <em>Skill in the right use of words comes from God</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:6–12:8</a> <em>Special abilities are given by God to believers.</em></p>",
